    title: "Financial Fee Management",
    text: "It is the safe financial and accounting management for all registrations, student installments, remaining fees and other printing of invoices and bonds",
  },
  {
    svg: "person",
    title: "Attendance",
    text: "The preparation process has now become easy, smooth and without errors, as the system provides the possibility of preparing students directly in the classroom via a tablet or mobile device via the network.",
  },
  {
    svg: "bus",
    title: "deportation",
    text: "The system contains a management tracking and monitoring the process of transferring students to and from school, in which all details and routes of the bus are clarified",
  },
  {
    svg: "calendar",
    title: "School Schedule",
    text: "The possibility of creating and preparing the study schedule for all academic levels with ease and organizing it in an orderly manner with the ability for parents to view the study schedule online",
